				<img class="hvres-variant-img lazy" data-original="/pic/kt/MZkcEdU_2K5al29t-OZj1g.gif" /></span></div><p class="hvres-source">Dị thể</p>		<div class="hvres-meaning"><a href="/whv/组"><span class="hvres-variant han">&#32452;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>		<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-16/poem-BNgl-5l_4eNXIeLJyIXT-g">Cảm ngộ kỳ 16 - 感遇其十六</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Can-mao-2/poem-sa85iEQrSGk1mnTgBoNSDQ">Can mao 2 - 干旄 2</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/H%E1%BB%91i-nh%E1%BA%ADt-du-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-L%C3%BD-Vi-Khanh-th%C3%A0nh-nam-bi%E1%BB%87t-nghi%E1%BB%87p-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-vVByMVS7AqtPaCdyYZrTjg">Hối nhật du Đại Lý Vi Khanh thành nam biệt nghiệp kỳ 4 - 晦日遊大理韋卿城南別業其四</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/Kh%C3%AA-c%C6%B0/poem-RmUM3x84GiKq_JcQ11UInw">Khê cư - 溪居</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-cFCa0wn9ZwJZJ5nwtlsQmQ">Liễu Tông Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Bao-H%C3%A0/K%C3%BD-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BB%8B-Ng%E1%BB%B1/poem-MJj7Ul46OyEhrPupOHIeiw">Ký Dương Thị Ngự - 寄楊侍御</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Bao-H%C3%A0/author-Al1aHrGQTzcKkvfhPwdKFA">Bao Hà</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2u-Vi/L%C6%B0u-bi%E1%BB%87t-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/poem-Sm6raO-tD